---
// Quote.astro - Simple quote section
---

<section class="quote-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Did you know?</h2>
    <p>
      When you order through Eatables, you're not just making your life easier. You're
      supporting thousands of local businesses, helping delivery partners earn a living, and
      contributing to the growth of your local community. Every order makes a difference.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .quote-section {
    background: #F8F8F8;
    padding: 80px 0px;
margin: 0px 60px;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .quote-section h2 {
    font-family: "Unbounded", sans-serif;
    font-optical-sizing: auto;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 30px;
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .quote-section p {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #202125;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Responsive design */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .quote-section {
      padding: 60px 0;
margin: 0px 0px;
    }

    .container {
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }

    .quote-section h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .quote-section p {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .quote-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .quote-section p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  }
</style>
